					<div class="pkg-tag">CORE</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 04</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/tdd <em>the red bar</em></div>
					<div class="pkg-desc">Enforces red-green-refactor. No implementation commits until a failing test exists. Works with vitest, bun test, jest, pytest.</div>
					<div class="pkg-tag">CORE</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 05</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/ci <em>the gate</em></div>
