					<div class="pkg-tag">PLUGIN</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 11</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/cli <em>the standalone</em></div>
					<div class="pkg-desc">Terminal-native agent with everything wired in. API keys or OAuth; works without Claude Code.</div>
					<div class="pkg-tag">CLI</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 12</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/ai <em>the primitives</em></div>
					<div class="pkg-desc">Unified API for OpenAI, Anthropic, Google &amp; fourteen others. Streaming, tools, thinking levels, cache control.</div>
					<div class="pkg-tag">LIBRARY</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 13</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/extensions <em>the slots</em></div>
					<div class="pkg-desc">Extension host — skills, prompt packs, custom tools, UI panels. Everything bendable is a TypeScript module.</div>
					<div class="pkg-tag">LIBRARY</div>
				</a>
				<a class="pkg" href="https://github.com/draht-dev/draht">
					<span class="pkg-idx">№ 14</span>
					<div class="pkg-name">@draht/tui <em>the loom</em></div>
